MangaBoya Privacy Policy 

iOS Version: MangaBoya for iOS does not collect any user information


Android Version: 
By default, MangaBoya does not collect any user information. 
If you choose to sign in with Google for data synchronization, we will only collect necessary account information for sync functionality. 
This login is optional and not required for normal app usage. 

We commit to: 
1) Only use your information for data synchronization purposes 
2) Never share your information with third parties 
3) You can delete your account and all synced data at any time.
